                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-8">
                                    <p>
                                    Indulge in the luxurious experience of a Moroccan bath at our salon, designed to cleanse and revitalize your skin. Our Moroccan bath includes a traditional steam treatment that opens pores and prepares your skin for deep cleansing. Following the steam, a gentle exfoliating scrub removes dead skin cells and reveals a smoother, more radiant complexion.

                                    </p>
                                    <p>
                                    The ritual continues with a hydrating and moisturizing treatment that leaves your skin feeling soft and nourished. Our Moroccan bath experience combines traditional techniques with modern comforts, providing a soothing and rejuvenating experience that enhances your overall sense of well-being.
